New Tuesday Tip on Video: learn how to quickly and easily optimize Your YouTube Videos! - Juan 

In this video you'll learn:

#1. how to use keywords with less competition;
#2. what to name your filename and how to upload an enticing Image thumbnail for your Video;
#3. what keywords to use in your title, description and meta tags.

For more #video tips, check out the related article http://bit.ly/optimize-youtube-video - credits to MarketingProfs. How to Quickly Optimize Your YouTube Video.
